title: Gold Tumbles After Release of Fed Minutes
description:
April 10 (Bloomberg) -- Several members of the Federal Open Market Committee said the central bank should begin tapering its bond buying program later this year and stop it by year end. Wells Fargo Funds Management Chief Portfolio Strategist Brian Jacobsen speaks on Bloomberg Television's "In The Loop." (Source: Bloomberg)
